snippet.title: Burger King: CD-i Training (Philips CD-i, 1997) *Upscaled,no subs version pinned in comments*
snippet.description:
Let's talk about old games on mah discord https://discord.gg/eBee7UG7t7


Big thanks to KalioKyra for dumping this disc!
http://redump.org/disc/87268/


https://twitter.com/KailoKyra/status/1465320473869357056

Burger King: CD-i Training: November, 1997

This is a fmv rip, it has some crashing issues in cdiemu even with all the bios roms. Bored and want to support the channel so I can buy a laptop that can emulate PS2 fan translations?. well here you go!

Paypal: https://www.paypal.me/consolescenenews

Thank you very much!
